Rules-Requires-Root: binary-targets

Package: cloudflare-ip-updater
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ruby (>= 2.0), systemd
Description: Automatic DNS updater for Cloudflare domains
 This tool monitors your external IP address and automatically updates
 your Cloudflare DNS records when it changes.
 .
 The service runs via systemd timer every 3 hours, checking for IP changes
 and updating the configured DNS record accordingly.
 .
 Configuration is stored in /etc/cloudflare-ip-updater/config